name: The Gosford Stool
description: The Gosford stool is a classic DAVIDSON design, exuding quality, and class, making it an exceptional finishing touch to a bedroom or dressing room. With its slender tapered legs meeting the luxurious appeal of the deep buttoning and plush padding, this stool offers the perfect balance of grace and luxury. The legs are finished in a dark tinted beech that speaks of a refined sophistication and contrasts pleasingly with Beaumont & Fletcher's opulent upholstery fabric. Like the rest of the chairs from the collection, the Gosford can be upholstered in any fabric to suit your interior.
